{"tid":1878023,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 7 最終更新後頻現死機　用戶無法正常關閉電腦","createTime":"2020-02-13T10:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T07:04:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d756d5393f3588d101c642a657bcc53d388d0724","tid":1878023,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"在上月 14 日，Microsoft 已經正式終止對 Windows 7 的支援，官方不會對 Windows 7 的用戶提供主流和安全性更新。然而，有用戶就投訴安裝 Windows 7 的最終更新後，不能如常地進行關機或重開機程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/13/microsoft-windows7/wireless-home/desktop-pc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F13%2Fmicrosoft-windows7%2Fwireless-home%2Fdesktop-pc%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5Ivb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=13dd2671\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/13/microsoft-windows7/wireless-home/desktop-pc/</a>"},{"pid":"29487a7bef739c3d3724625a9708299e50fc6125","tid":1878023,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"在 Microsoft 的論壇、Reddit 和其他討論區中，也有 Windows 7 用戶報告，進行最後一次更新後，電腦經常出現死機的情況；電腦後來更加彈出「您沒有關閉這台電腦的權限」的訊息，讓用戶無法關機或重啟電腦。"},{"pid":"af2e6f3902d24d34321bff33c35f8c69780d9db8","tid":1878023,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"部分用戶稱只要關閉 Adobe 的更新服務便能夠關機。有猜測指用戶有機會是因為某個問題違反了用戶帳號控制（User Account Control）的群組政策，或者是最新 Windows 7 Rollup 更新出錯。"},{"pid":"78d14d99fcb5a679ed1ecf4417ed150ded87c3df","tid":1878023,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:55:39.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 在向 Bleeping Computer 提供的聲明中表示，他們正在積極地調查漏洞，但現在尚未清楚官方將會採取甚麼行動。"},{"pid":"aa74317f8946178af371b96f3d4829d1d66d6fee","tid":1878023,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔升win10機都唔俾你關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf3930c0e6968cf1fe034e27e2498c6611eff1f","tid":1878023,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"迫你上win10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8daaefa57156fdcad1e54ab72996429d860cb85","tid":1878023,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"我都係用7<br />\n唔緊要，壞機就轉win10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab83aaeb4fcd06e0031405b1a4a28750cb358279","tid":1878023,"uid":155781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"on9 microsoft<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a38314f1934af5d0b44ac4dc9963cd895648b2c","tid":1878023,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"屌好似瀨咗嘢...而家部機開唔返"},{"pid":"ab17045b93580fd6dbb16e0620211d96f1480137","tid":1878023,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"用 linux"},{"pid":"67251fe8deb052222c173b762a698507da246d3a","tid":1878023,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"7093 被列入戰略物資<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1882208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1882208</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}